OL,7,FLorraine Griffin fears one of her sons
OL,8,Fmight not qualify for PIP under the
OL,9,Fplanned changes, Hannah Ludlow reports
OL,11,FA mother with two sons with autism has
OL,12,Fsaid the government's planned welfare
OL,13,Fchanges would devastate her family's
OL,14,Ffuture.
OL,16,FLorraine Griffin, from Dudley, relies
OL,17,Fon the Disability Living Allowance for
OL,18,Fher boys, Sam and Ben, aged 12 and 13.
