OL,7,FLorraine faces constant costs -
OL,8,Fmedicine, nappies for Ben, who has
OL,9,Fmore severe autism, and replacing TVs
OL,10,Fhe has broken.
OL,12,FWhen they reach 16, they will need to
OL,13,Fapply for Personal Independence
OL,14,FPayment (PIP).
OL,16,FBut news that their benefits could be
OL,17,Fat risk led to her being hospitalised
OL,18,Ffrom stress.
