OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FMs Griffin said: "If they attack these
OL,8,Fbenefits, these payments that are our
OL,9,Flife, where on Earth will we be?
OL,11,F"I ended up in A&E because of my
OL,12,Fheartbeat going absolutely crazy. This
OL,13,Fis everything to me, this is our life,
OL,14,FI'm repsonsible for these boys, I'm
OL,15,Fresponsible for everything they have
OL,16,Fin life."
OL,18,FThe Universal Credit and Personal
OL,19,FIndependence Payment Bill is set to be
OL,20,Fvoted on by MPs next Tuesday.
