OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FIt would make it harder for disabled
OL,8,Fpeople with less severe conditions to
OL,9,Fclaim PIP.
OL,11,F"Isn't life hard enough? We have got
OL,12,Fthat much to process and to put up
OL,13,Fwith in our daily lives, it just makes
OL,14,Flife impossible, what they're taking
OL,15,Faway from us," Ms Griffin said.
OL,17,FShe added: "Why are they rushing into
OL,18,Fthis, to do it now? Do it properly.
OL,19,FFind out what families need. Come and
OL,20,Ftake a look, just slow down. Please
OL,21,Fdon't, don't cut off our livelihood."
