OL,7,FThose applying have to declare how
OL,8,Fcomplex their needs are in a list of
OL,9,F10 daily activities:
OL,11,FThey get points for each category, the
OL,12,Fhigher the number, the more restricted
OL,13,Fthe person is.
OL,15,FUnder the current system, you need to
OL,16,Fscore at least 8 points in total to
OL,17,Freceive the 'standard rate' of funding
OL,18,Ffor the 'daily living' component.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
