OL,3,CMum of sons with autism hospitalised
OL,4,Cdue to fears of losing disability
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FUnder the new system, from November
OL,8,F2026, you will still need to get at
OL,9,Fleast 8 points - but 4 of those need
OL,10,Fto come from at least one daily living
OL,11,Factivity.
OL,13,FThe other part of PIP - the funding
OL,14,Ffor 'mobility' - will not be affected.
OL,16,FThe welfare reforms also include
OL,17,Fchanges to Universal Credit, and more
OL,18,Fface-to-face assessments.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
