OL,7,FThere is a growing rebellion in
OL,8,FParliament with Labour MPs challenging
OL,9,Fthe planned reforms. More than a 100
OL,10,FLabour MPs a publicly backing a move
OL,11,Fto block the legislation.
OL,13,FBut Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,14,Fhas said: "We have got to make the
OL,15,Freforms to our system. It isn't
OL,16,Fworking as it is.
OL,18,F"It doesn't work as it stands for
OL,19,Fpeople who desperately need help to
OL,20,Fget into work or for people who need
OL,21,Fprotection. It is broken.
